#Shifting Shadow (#1085): aura. At my upkeep destroy the enchanted creature,
#reveal until a creature, put it onto my battlefield (shadow rehooks), bottom
#the rest. Bears die T3; reveal = millstone then hill giant; giant lands on my
#side, millstone goes to the bottom.
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
manapool:{2}{R}
hand:shifting shadow
inplay:grizzly bears
library:hill giant,millstone
[PLAYER2]
library:darksteel citadel,juggernaut
[DO]
shifting shadow
grizzly bears
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
goto end
goto firstmain
goto end
goto upkeep
goto upkeep
choice 0
goto upkeep
hill giant
goto upkeep
goto upkeep
choice 1
goto upkeep
millstone
goto upkeep
goto upkeep
[ASSERT]
UPKEEP
[PLAYER1]
graveyard:grizzly bears
inplay:shifting shadow,hill giant
library:millstone
[PLAYER2]
hand:juggernaut
library:darksteel citadel
[END]
#PARKED: reveal-machinery family (selvalas_charge/enforcer cousins) + aura
#lifecycle wrinkle. Trace: upkeep trigger resolves, destroy leg kills the bears,
#but the AURA goes to the graveyard with them (SBA before rehook can happen).
#choice 0 DOES fire a second StackAbility (the optionone choice exists and
#resolves) but target(creature|reveal) moveto(mybattlefield) moves nothing -
#the Reveal:1/revealuntil(creature) zone was never populated (library unchanged,
#both cards still there). choice 1 + millstone click inert. Engine round fuel:
#reveal-conditional machinery + revealuntil + aura-rehook-vs-SBA ordering.
